cdata.name: BlockCAT
cdata.desc:
BlockCAT, short for Blockchain Complex Automated Transactions, is an Ethereum-based decentralized platform that provides an easy to use web portal for end users and organizations to provision and deploy smart contracts without the need to have prior knowledge or expertise.

The BlockCAT marketplace allowsanyone to contribute and sell smart contracts, while thecustom designed contract auditing system keeps users safe from faulty contracts in a completely decentralized manner. The CAT token will be used on the platform as theonly means of paying for contract deployment.
